1
00:01:44,320 --> 00:01:45,450
I came here this time

2
00:01:46,280 --> 00:01:48,400
mainly to report something to you.

3
00:01:48,640 --> 00:01:49,000
Oh.

4
00:01:50,000 --> 00:01:54,039
I specifically selected some of Xiaoyue's best works

5
00:01:54,520 --> 00:01:56,840
to display at the art exhibition.

6
00:01:57,640 --> 00:01:59,240
I... I am blind.

7
00:01:59,240 --> 00:02:00,120
I can't see.

8
00:02:00,120 --> 00:02:01,180
It's fine, Auntie.

9
00:02:02,600 --> 00:02:04,040
Even if you can't see,

10
00:02:04,760 --> 00:02:06,240
we artists believe that

11
00:02:06,920 --> 00:02:08,449
by feeling with your heart,

12
00:02:09,000 --> 00:02:11,130
you can still appreciate the artwork.

13
00:02:11,280 --> 00:02:14,040
This is the meaning of our artwork.

14
00:02:14,040 --> 00:02:15,520
I'm begging you.

15
00:02:15,520 --> 00:02:16,320
Right?

16
00:02:16,720 --> 00:02:17,280
I'm begging you.

17
00:02:17,280 --> 00:02:18,880
Why are there so many?

18
00:02:18,880 --> 00:02:20,880
Why don't we let Xiaoyue take a look?

19
00:02:21,160 --> 00:02:22,000
No need.

20
00:02:22,640 --> 00:02:24,370
These are Xiaoyue's own works.

21
00:02:25,440 --> 00:02:26,900
She has already seen them.

22
00:02:27,560 --> 00:02:29,880
Xiaoyue, do you want to take another look?

23
00:02:29,880 --> 00:02:30,600
Have a look.

24
00:02:30,600 --> 00:02:31,120
All right.

25
00:02:31,120 --> 00:02:33,320
Auntie, I'll let her take another look.

26
00:02:38,240 --> 00:02:39,000
Xiaoyue.

27
00:02:43,160 --> 00:02:44,040
Teacher.

28
00:02:44,040 --> 00:02:45,520
These are the ones selected.

29
00:02:45,520 --> 00:02:46,520
What do you think?

30
00:02:48,120 --> 00:02:50,240
These are the ones I really like.

31
00:02:52,400 --> 00:02:53,200
Xiaoyue,

32
00:02:54,000 --> 00:02:55,530
are they really beautiful?

33
00:02:55,640 --> 00:02:57,120
Tell Mom about them.

34
00:02:57,120 --> 00:02:58,280
Of course they are.

35
00:03:00,640 --> 00:03:01,840
Hurry up and tell Auntie.

36
00:03:01,840 --> 00:03:03,500
They are very beautiful, Mom.

37
00:03:03,560 --> 00:03:04,680
Then hurry up

38
00:03:04,680 --> 00:03:06,010
and thank your teacher.

39
00:03:06,400 --> 00:03:07,880
It's what I should do.

40
00:03:12,600 --> 00:03:13,120
Auntie,

41
00:03:13,960 --> 00:03:15,280
Qiaoyue is moved to tears.

42
00:03:15,280 --> 00:03:15,880
Is that so?

43
00:03:17,200 --> 00:03:19,400
It's all because you are a good teacher.

44
00:03:19,640 --> 00:03:20,360
Xiaoyue,

45
00:03:21,600 --> 00:03:23,840
you must thank your teacher properly.

46
00:03:25,280 --> 00:03:26,640
I think for Xiaoyue,

47
00:03:27,160 --> 00:03:29,680
if she continues studying like this,

48
00:03:31,120 --> 00:03:34,960
she will definitely have a bright future.

49
00:03:36,040 --> 00:03:37,200
Okay.

50
00:03:37,200 --> 00:03:37,960
Thank you.

51
00:03:38,040 --> 00:03:38,640
Auntie,

52
00:03:38,640 --> 00:03:39,770
I'll be leaving now.

53
00:03:40,280 --> 00:03:41,079
Okay.

54
00:03:58,200 --> 00:03:59,840
Hey, Qiaoyue.

55
00:04:00,400 --> 00:04:01,160
I'm sorry.

56
00:04:01,560 --> 00:04:02,760
I was wrong before.

57
00:04:04,040 --> 00:04:05,120
I miss you.

58
00:04:06,120 --> 00:04:07,080
I'll go find you.

59
00:04:07,600 --> 00:04:08,880
I don't want to see you right now.

60
00:04:08,880 --> 00:04:09,810
Don't come over.

61
00:04:10,720 --> 00:04:11,480
Qiaoyue.

62
00:04:12,840 --> 00:04:14,500
What exactly happened to you?

63
00:04:19,000 --> 00:04:20,279
Allen, let's break up.

64
00:04:21,320 --> 00:04:22,320
I'm really tired.

65
00:04:22,720 --> 00:04:24,360
Are you crazy?

66
00:04:24,800 --> 00:04:26,120
Let's just leave it at that.

67
00:04:26,120 --> 00:04:26,800
Qiaoyue.

68
00:04:35,520 --> 00:04:36,520
Xiaoyue.

69
00:04:39,000 --> 00:04:40,200
You're not asleep yet, are you?

70
00:04:40,200 --> 00:04:40,880
Not yet.

71
00:04:40,880 --> 00:04:41,680
What's wrong?

72
00:04:45,920 --> 00:04:47,120
Let me tell you.

73
00:04:51,200 --> 00:04:52,000
What's wrong?

74
00:04:53,560 --> 00:04:54,600
Xiaoyue.

75
00:04:55,080 --> 00:04:56,200
Mr. Mu said

76
00:04:56,200 --> 00:04:58,860
he wants to put your painting in the exhibition.

77
00:04:59,760 --> 00:05:00,920
You've made something of yourself.

78
00:05:00,920 --> 00:05:02,360
I am so happy.

79
00:05:02,880 --> 00:05:05,200
I just don't know how to thank him.

80
00:05:05,920 --> 00:05:07,120
I picked these fruits

81
00:05:07,160 --> 00:05:08,760
with my own hands.

82
00:05:09,600 --> 00:05:11,200
You should take them to him.

83
00:05:18,440 --> 00:05:20,040
You are so outstanding.

84
00:05:20,240 --> 00:05:21,880
I am really proud.

85
00:05:27,920 --> 00:05:28,960
Honey.

86
00:05:29,880 --> 00:05:31,760
Honey, it's really urgent.

87
00:05:32,640 --> 00:05:33,920
Listen to me.

88
00:05:35,240 --> 00:05:37,040
I really have something urgent to tell you.

89
00:05:37,040 --> 00:05:38,000
Spit it out.

90
00:05:38,000 --> 00:05:38,880
I'm in a hurry.

91
00:05:48,920 --> 00:05:49,640
Go ahead.

92
00:05:51,240 --> 00:05:53,100
I've run out of my creative funds.

93
00:05:55,200 --> 00:05:55,720
But

94
00:05:56,800 --> 00:05:58,280
I've finished my artwork.

95
00:05:58,280 --> 00:06:00,600
It will definitely fetch a good price this time.

96
00:06:00,600 --> 00:06:01,520
You know,

97
00:06:01,640 --> 00:06:03,500
creation requires inspiration.

98
00:06:03,520 --> 00:06:05,520
Inspiration needs to be found.

99
00:06:06,040 --> 00:06:08,760
Finding inspiration means experiencing life,

100
00:06:09,320 --> 00:06:10,980
which requires money, right?

101
00:06:12,480 --> 00:06:13,800
Experiencing life?

102
00:06:14,960 --> 00:06:16,240
Don't think I don't know

103
00:06:16,240 --> 00:06:17,880
what you did with that money.

104
00:06:18,880 --> 00:06:20,140
You can play with fire,

105
00:06:20,760 --> 00:06:21,890
but don't go too far.

106
00:06:23,160 --> 00:06:26,480
Be careful, your little heart might not be able to take it.

107
00:06:29,400 --> 00:06:30,240
Don't worry.

108
00:06:31,560 --> 00:06:33,220
I'll take my medicine on time.

109
00:06:34,360 --> 00:06:35,159
All right.

110
00:06:35,440 --> 00:06:37,960
I'll arrange for finance to wire you the money tomorrow.

111
00:06:37,960 --> 00:06:39,000
Thank you, honey.

112
00:06:40,480 --> 00:06:42,080
I'm in a hurry. I have to go.

113
00:06:49,240 --> 00:06:50,880
There's no one else here.

114
00:06:51,159 --> 00:06:53,490
Who are you showing off your affection to?

115
00:06:54,040 --> 00:06:54,960
Mr. Mu.

116
00:07:00,080 --> 00:07:00,680
Honey.

117
00:07:00,920 --> 00:07:01,920
I'll leave you to your work.

118
00:07:01,920 --> 00:07:02,850
I'm leaving now.

119
00:07:04,520 --> 00:07:05,480
Be careful.

120
00:07:16,680 --> 00:07:19,140
This is the fruit my mom asked me to bring you.

121
00:07:23,000 --> 00:07:23,280
I...

122
00:07:23,960 --> 00:07:25,490
I want to drop out of school.

123
00:07:48,960 --> 00:07:51,890
Have I been treating you too well these past few days?

124
00:07:52,840 --> 00:07:54,700
How dare you speak to me like that.

125
00:07:56,280 --> 00:07:58,440
Do you also look down on me?

126
00:07:59,720 --> 00:08:00,650
I'm telling you.

127
00:08:01,400 --> 00:08:02,860
When my work is completed,

128
00:08:03,960 --> 00:08:06,920
I'll make everyone who looks down on me regret it.

129
00:09:36,960 --> 00:09:37,720
Wait for me.

130
00:10:26,360 --> 00:10:27,680
I sympathize with your situation,

131
00:10:27,680 --> 00:10:29,340
and I understand how you feel.

132
00:10:30,360 --> 00:10:31,760
But I am a police officer.

133
00:10:32,160 --> 00:10:33,420
The law shows no mercy.

134
00:10:34,240 --> 00:10:35,840
If he broke the law,

135
00:10:36,160 --> 00:10:37,520
the law will punish him.

136
00:10:37,520 --> 00:10:39,920
He will definitely receive the punishment he deserves.

137
00:10:39,920 --> 00:10:40,560
But you

138
00:10:40,840 --> 00:10:42,560
chose to fight evil with evil.

139
00:10:42,800 --> 00:10:43,800
Now look,

140
00:10:44,560 --> 00:10:46,400
we can only arrest you.

141
00:10:48,400 --> 00:10:50,000
Fight evil with evil.

142
00:10:50,280 --> 00:10:51,240
Arrest me.

143
00:10:52,480 --> 00:10:53,410
Officer Zhuang.

144
00:10:53,920 --> 00:10:55,580
I didn't break any laws, did I?

145
00:10:55,880 --> 00:10:57,720
Did I commit murder or arson?

146
00:10:58,520 --> 00:11:01,200
Mu Weijie is the one who broke the law.

147
00:11:01,640 --> 00:11:03,080
He committed rape,

148
00:11:03,480 --> 00:11:04,640
date rape,

149
00:11:05,160 --> 00:11:06,160
intimidation,

150
00:11:06,880 --> 00:11:08,360
and false imprisonment.

151
00:11:09,080 --> 00:11:11,360
He is the one you should be arresting.

152
00:11:11,920 --> 00:11:12,800
Whether we arrest him or not

153
00:11:12,800 --> 00:11:15,000
and how we do it is none of your business.

154
00:11:15,400 --> 00:11:17,760
Right now, all you need to do is cooperate.

155
00:11:22,800 --> 00:11:25,060
You've already closed this case, right?

156
00:11:25,160 --> 00:11:26,640
Closed as an accident.

157
00:11:29,560 --> 00:11:31,680
You caused all these accidents.

158
00:11:32,160 --> 00:11:33,280
Because you knew

159
00:11:33,560 --> 00:11:35,040
if you called the police,

160
00:11:35,280 --> 00:11:37,400
Mu Weijie would fight back desperately.

161
00:11:37,400 --> 00:11:39,200
But if you killed him yourself,

162
00:11:40,000 --> 00:11:41,960
you would be punished by the law.

163
00:11:42,280 --> 00:11:43,000
So,

164
00:11:43,000 --> 00:11:45,360
you created all these accidents.

165
00:11:49,640 --> 00:11:51,560
I pulled off an accident.

166
00:11:52,920 --> 00:11:54,800
I'm so amazing.

167
00:11:56,960 --> 00:11:58,220
Where is the evidence?

168
00:12:01,080 --> 00:12:03,200
I don't think I'm that capable.

169
00:12:04,200 --> 00:12:05,080
Of course you are.
